caption.text:
They met as teenagers in a jazz youth club. Today they’re the award-winning music group @ezracollective (Ezra Collective). 🥁🎷🎸🎺🎹
 
“It typically starts with a voice note,” says lead drummer Femi describing Ezra Collective’s creative process. “The beauty of being a band is the initial idea is one thing, but we all get our moment to interpret whatever that idea is. I get excited to hear what Joe is going to do to the initial ideas I had, and what James is going to add, and TJ is going to change. And that’s what makes us — that’s what’s exciting about it.”
 
In this edition of The Creative Process, step into the studio as Femi, TJ, Ife, Joe and James bring an all-new improvised track to life and create an original, never-before-heard song.
 
“This moment we’ve just had here, just in this room, it’s been one of my favorite moments playing with the boys in ages. It’s just a lot of gratefulness and joy all mixed together. And I think that’s what people feel when they come to the concerts. The party starts on the stage and everyone is invited.” 🎶💗🎶
 
Music by @ezracollective

caption.text:
“If I like something, I wear it.”

Multimedia artist @ava_ark’s (Ava Kalitowski) short, snappy video edits highlight her love of secondhand fashion.

“I find that my unfussed editing style draws people in because it keeps my content natural and relatable — and shares an authentic, unfiltered window into my life. 

Dressing in a fun, characterful way means I live a bigger and richer life when I enter the outside world. There’s a certain level of confidence you gain when you allow yourself to wear exactly what you desire.”

Video by @ava_ark

caption.text:
“What I love about March Madness is that anything can happen out there. If you’re a dog, you’ll survive.” —@haileyvanlith (Hailey Van Lith)

For today’s episode of #10Things, we caught up with the @tcuwbb guard as she was preparing for her fourth career NCAA women’s basketball tournament, on the heels of helping her team secure a Big 12 Championship. 
 
1. 👟 + 🏀 = 🔥
2. POV HVL
3. From the court to the closet 👚
4. Business chic with a side of streetwear ✔️ 
5. #fearless 
6. 🧩😮 
7. Teatime 
8. A tribute to Kobe (🎨: @jaydanoblewilliams) 
9. Putting in the work 🏋️‍♀️ 
10. Center circle sign-off ✌️

caption.text:
She ate and left no crumbs 🍽️✂️✨

Artist @papereatsss (PaperEats) knows how to make food that looks — and sounds — delicious. “I want people to feel happy and pull out their inner child when they watch my videos. Take in the nostalgia and feel a spark of joy that makes the want to create.”

With every tiny detail of her food replicas, PaperEats transforms paper and combines it with ASMR-worthy sound to create something magical. “Artists all have one thing in common: we can make something out of nothing!”

Video by @papereatsss

Join model and creator @jake.fleming (Jake Fleming) as he visits the Versace HQ during Milan Fashion Week to meet his idol @donatella_versace (Donatella Versace) in person for the first time after connecting on DMs. 🌟

caption.text:
Be your own muse. 🙃

Free spirit @kittylever (Kitty Lever) loves inspiring others to indulge in the whimsical.

“My approach to creating is really just living curiously and staying open to capturing it. I say yes to experiences. I wear outfits that portray how I’m feeling on the inside. When I post something, I am putting a piece of myself in the world.” 🎀💗

Video by @kittylever
